cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on person re-identification using deep learning models, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also mention modifications to the network architecture and training process, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on public datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) as person re-identification has applications in surveillance and security.
